Curated indicator values (data/raw/curated_indicators.csv) are derived from
publicly available scholarly and registry sources cited in the file's
provenance column and in data/raw/curated_indicators_README.md. World Bank
data are released under CC BY 4.0 by the original publisher. CONCORD-3
survival values are extracted from an open-access Lancet article (Allemani
et al. 2018) and re-published here for analytic reproducibility under fair
use; please cite the original paper.
